{"id":29636693071,"name":"Run api tests","node_id":"WFR_kwLOA_1uaM8AAAAG5nwMTw","head_branch":"perf/geofeatures-geom-prefilter-43_2.43","head_sha":"116fb08e3eeeb16a2aef5c3a7684d450fcbdec5c","path":".github/workflows/run-api-tests.yml","run_number":51194,"run_attempt":1,"event":"pull_request","display_title":"backport: perf: pre-filter geoFeatures org units by geometry","status":"completed","conclusion":"success","workflow_id":5591308,"check_suite_id":80260717648,"check_suite_node_id":"CS_kwDOA_1uaM8AAAASr-lcUA","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29636693071","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29636693071","pull_requests":[{"id":4081622337,"number":24491,"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/pulls/24491","head":{"ref":"perf/geofeatures-geom-prefilter-43_2.43","sha":"116fb08e3eeeb16a2aef5c3a7684d450fcbdec5c","repo":{"id":66940520,"name":"dhis2-core","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core"}},"base":{"ref":"2.43","sha":"d66adbdec7c27ec8758456a9bbf6ff44bfe4d5ba","repo":{"id":66940520,"name":"dhis2-core","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core"}}}],"created_at":"2026-07-18T07:59:44Z","updated_at":"2026-07-18T08:12:18Z","run_started_at":"2026-07-18T07:59:44Z","jobs_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29636693071/jobs","logs_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29636693071/logs","check_suite_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/check-suites/80260717648","artifacts_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29636693071/artifacts","cancel_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29636693071/cancel","rerun_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29636693071/rerun","head_commit":{"message":"perf: pre-filter geoFeatures org units by geometry (#24279)\n\n* perf: pre-filter geoFeatures org units by geometry\n\ngeoFeatures resolves the `ou` dimension into full OrganisationUnit\nentities, then discards every unit without geometry in-memory. On a\nlarge hierarchy (Nigeria prod: ~255k level-5 units, all null-geometry)\nthis hydrates a quarter-million entities — ~7.6s CPU and ~4.7 GB\nallocated — only to return [].\n\nThread an optional `geometryOnly` flag from DataQueryRequest through\nDimensionalObjectProvider and OrganisationUnitService down to\nHibernateOrganisationUnitStore, which appends `and o.geometry is not\nnull`. Default off, so all other callers dispatch the original 2-arg\nmethods unchanged. Skipped in geoJsonAttribute (coordinateField) mode,\nwhere coordinates come from an attribute and the geometry column may be\nnull. The in-memory filter remains the precise final gate.\n\nWhen the geometry-filtered resolution is empty, the E7143 empty-dimension\nguard is suppressed so geoFeatures still returns 200 [] rather than an\nerror.\n\nValidated on production (Nigeria, deployed on 2.40): a comparable\nhigh-level layer dropped from ~8.6s/4.7GB to 14ms/747KB.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 (1M context) \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e\n\n* refactor: bundle getDimension args into DimensionResolveOptions\n\nThe private getDimension dispatcher grew to 8 parameters when geometryOnly\nwas threaded through, tripping SonarQube java:S107 (\u003e7 parameters). Bundle\nthe five resolution options (relativePeriodDate, displayProperty, allowNull,\ninputIdScheme, geometryOnly) into a private DimensionResolveOptions record,\nbringing the method to 4 parameters. Behaviour is unchanged; contained\nentirely within DefaultDataQueryService.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 (1M context) \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e\n\n---------\n\nCo-authored-by: Claude Opus 4.8 (1M context) \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e","author":{"name":"Jason Pickering","email":"jason@dhis2.org"},"id":"116fb08e3eeeb16a2aef5c3a7684d450fcbdec5c","tree_id":"56cdb24e7f0654434456ae24a950ca4fa17be61b","timestamp":"2026-07-18T07:59:35Z","committ